headline.print_headline: German Raider Protectionist Wins Melbourne Cup
headline.main: German Raider Protectionist Wins Melbourne Cup

lead_paragraph: German raider Protectionist timed his finishing burst to perfection to win the 154th running of the A$6.2 million ($5.38 million) Melbourne Cup at Flemington Racecourse on Tuesday.
